{"lastModified":1772145353204,"uri":"c::51632648983::vessel::cd1b0ff0-11bd-11f1-b8d4-ebaad6669375","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area:Key West, Florida, USA, Fort Lauderdale, Miami\n\nThe Lagoon 450 F (flybridge) barely needs an introduction as it is one of the most popular mid-sized catamarans on the secondhand market. Safe and easy for a couple to handle but large enough for entertaining in style and comfort.\n\nHighlights include a spacious cockpit, excellent flybridge visibility, and a forward cockpit for panoramic views and cooling breezes. Below deck, four bright ensuite cabins offer generous headroom, while a well-designed galley and light-filled saloon with seamless deck access complete this sought-after cruising catamaran.","blueprint":{"name":"SOMEWHERE","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::cd1b0ff0-11bd-11f1-b8d4-ebaad6669375::assets::7d068b91-11c0-11f1-9a63-a9a8d8f336a0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::cd1b0ff0-11bd-11f1-b8d4-ebaad6669375::assets::7d052c00-11c0-11f1-9a63-a9a8d8f336a0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::cd1b0ff0-11bd-11f1-b8d4-ebaad6669375::assets::7d035740-11c0-11f1-9a63-a9a8d8f336a0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::cd1b0ff0-11bd-11f1-b8d4-ebaad6669375::assets::7d052c01-11c0-11f1-9a63-a9a8d8f336a0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::cd1b0ff0-11bd-11f1-b8d4-ebaad6669375::assets::7cf99340-11c0-11f1-9a62-a9a8d8f336a0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::cd1b0ff0-11bd-11f1-b8d4-ebaad6669375::assets::7d052c02-11c0-11f1-9a63-a9a8d8f336a0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::cd1b0ff0-11bd-11f1-b8d4-ebaad6669375::assets::7d0293f0-11c0-11f1-9a63-a9a8d8f336a0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::cd1b0ff0-11bd-11f1-b8d4-ebaad6669375::assets::7cfa5690-11c0-11f1-9a63-a9a8d8f336a0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::cd1b0ff0-11bd-11f1-b8d4-ebaad6669375::assets::7d0727d0-11c0-11f1-9a63-a9a8d8f336a0/{imageVarian