"label":"Air Conditioning"},{"label":"Flybridge"},{"label":"Climate control in every cabin"},{"label":"Paddle Boards ","quantity":"2"}]},"crew":[{"name":"John R. Emlet","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::51632648983::vessel::cd1b0ff0-11bd-11f1-b8d4-ebaad6669375::assets::dc2c5f50-1346-11f1-99d7-e1918facef15/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"With over 50 years of boating experience, including four decades as a boat owner, Captain John is a seasoned maritime professional specializing in boat delivery, chartering, and international navigation. He has expertly handled vessels ranging from 36 to 125 feet, successfully navigating the waters of the Southeast U.S., the Caribbean, and South America."},{"name":"Amanda M. Emlet","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::51632648983::vessel::cd1b0ff0-11bd-11f1-b8d4-ebaad6669375::assets::3190b950-1347-11f1-886e-413f43c98a69/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"With years of hands-on experience in mooring operations, line handling, anchoring techniques, and vessel maintenance, Amanda plays a key role in keeping the yacht running smoothly. But beyond the deck, she’s equally passionate about guest service—whether it’s creating a welcoming atmosphere, assisting with excursions, or ensuring every detail is taken care of with precision."},{"name":"Cassandra Venter","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::51632648983::vessel::cd1b0ff0-11bd-11f1-b8d4-ebaad6669375::assets::2a2687d0-1347-11f1-886e-413f43c98a69/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Cassandra Venter is an experienced Chief Stewardess and Head Chef with a passion for delivering exceptional service in the luxury yachting industry. A South African native, Cassandra has built an impressive career aboard motor and sailing yachts ranging from 36 to 57 meters, working her way from stewardess to chief stewardess positions on prestigious vessels throughout the Bahamas, Fort Lauderdale, and Rhode Island. With extensive experience in high-level service, provisioning, interior management, and event coordination, Cassandra brings a unique blend of creativity and professionalism to every role. Her culinary skills complement her stewardess expertise, having served as crew chef on multiple vessels. Beyond yachting, she holds a Higher Professional Diploma in Fashion Design and brings artistic talents in graphic design, flower arrangement, and table décor to her work."}],"pricing":{"dayPricingFrom":{"currency":"USD","price":150000,"displayCurrency":"USD","displayPrice":150000,"unit":"HOUR"},"dayPricingTo":{"currency":"USD","price":450000,"displayCurrency":"USD","displayPrice":450000,"unit":"DAY"},"pricingInfo":[{"name":"2 Hours - Sunset Cruise","effectiveDates":[{"from":"2026-01-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2026-12-31T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2027-01-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2027-12-31T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2028-01-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2028-12-31T23:59:59.999Z"}],"pricing":{"currency":"USD","charterFee":150000,"inputAmountTaxed":"EXCLUSIVE","note":"","unit":"HOUR","lineItems":[{"item":"Charter Fee","quantity":1,"unitPrice":150000,"amount":150000,"conditions":"VAT & APA Excluded","taxRate":{"label":"VAT","value":0.075}}],"total":161250,"subTotal":150000,"totalTax":11250},"inclusionZones":[{"label":"Florida, US, United States","type":"State","category":["Florida"],"coordinates":[-83.13354787154184,28.36636070660095],"bbox":[-87.6074378816535,24.542349340056262,-80.04130722193477,31.00167331692866]},{"label":"United States of America","type":"Country","category":["North America","Northern America","United States of America"],"coordinates":[-52.64727122207621,46.84073876556497],"bbox":[-179.1435033839999,18.906117143000074,179.78093509200005,71.41250234600005]},{"label":"United States of America","type":"Geo subunit","category":["North America","Northern America","United States of America"],"coordinates":[-96.3420908403651,38.73256771297787],"bbox":[-124.7099609375,24.54233398437499,-66.98701171875,49.3696777343751]}],"exclusionZones":[],"petsAllowed":false},{"